45:28.560 --> 45:30.239
No, that's okay.

45:30.240 --> 45:34.347
I have been thinking about
that a bit this weekend,

45:35.440 --> 45:36.941
and

45:38.720 --> 45:40.870
I have no excuse.

45:42.680 --> 45:44.439
Of course I was insecure

45:44.440 --> 45:48.581
and of course we were
drifting apart at the time

45:48.640 --> 45:51.239
and instead of trying to communicate

45:51.240 --> 45:56.461
