47:39.480 --> 47:41.039
No.

47:41.040 --> 47:44.191
No, I was... Just seemed to...

47:48.520 --> 47:50.909
Is there anything you
want to talk about?

47:51.120 --> 47:52.359
No.

47:52.360 --> 47:55.559
There anything you
want to talk about?

47:55.560 --> 47:57.439
Look, this weekend is super weird...

