- That's okay, right?
- Yeah.

47:58.800 --> 48:02.986
I mean, you know,
I think it can be confusing,

48:03.880 --> 48:05.620
but I just...

48:06.600 --> 48:08.359
You know it's not real, right?

48:08.360 --> 48:13.024
I mean, I'm not that guy
out there doing sit-ups...

48:14.840 --> 48:21.279
