be really interested

48:21.280 --> 48:23.279
in some other version of you,

48:23.280 --> 48:26.919
knowing that my real
Sophie is here...

48:26.920 --> 48:29.439
- Right.
- And I just...

48:29.440 --> 48:31.639
I want to make sure you still agree.

48:31.640 --> 48:33.266
Yeah.

48:33.800 --> 48:35.381
Of course.

48:35.400 --> 48:36.479
- Okay.
- Yeah.

48:36.480 --> 48:37.639
Okay.

48:37.640 --> 48:39.141
[GIGGLES]

48:40.200 --> 48:42.159
- Okay. We good?
- Yeah, we're good.

48:42.160 --> 48:45.027
- Of course we're good.
- All right.

48:58.480 --> 49:00.391
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

49:05.120 --> 49:08.039
<i>Thanks a lot for calling me at two in
the morning. I really appreciate it.</i>

49:08.040 --> 49:10.599
<i>MAN: Like I don't have a job
to wake up for tomorrow.</i>

49:10.600 --> 49:13.399
<i>Maybe next time you can't
remember where you live,</i>

49:13.400 --> 49:15.159
<i>you should ask your wife.</i>

49:15.160 --> 49:16.639
<i>I'm not sure what you were doing</i>

49:16.640 --> 49:19.427
<i>at two in the morning anyway, but...</i>

49:20.240 --> 49:22.319
<i>WOMAN: Hey, Bunny. It's mama.</i>

49:22.320 --> 49:24.639
<i>I was just thinking about
our conversation yesterday.</i>

49:24.640 --> 49:25.719
<i>I don't know.</i>

49:25.720 --> 49:27.599
<i>You just didn't sound
like your usual self,</i>

49:27.600 --> 49:29.999
<i>so I just wanted to
be sure you're okay...</i>

49:30.000 --> 49:33.039
<i>MAN: Hey, man. The street
you grew up on was Berkman.</i>

49:33.040 --> 49:34.559
<i>Hope that clears things up.</i>

49:34.560 --> 49:36.585
<i>Talk to you soon.</i>

49:46.680 --> 49:48.119
Hey.

49:48.120 --> 49:49.701
- Hey.
- Um...

49:49.960 --> 49:52.559
So something really
weird just happened.

49:52.560 --> 49:56.679
I got a bunch of voice mails
from my mom and Doug and Dave

49:56.680 --> 50:00.502
saying I had called them
asking really weird questions,

50:00.800 --> 50:03.382
but I didn't call them.

50:03.680 --> 50:06.159
- That is weird.
- Yeah.

50:06.160 --> 50:08.319
Do you think you pocket dialed them?

50:08.320 --> 50:10.879
I don't think the pocket
dial makes as much sense

50:10.880 --> 50:13.159
because I was talking
and asking questions.

50:13.160 --> 50:15.981
- I would have...
- So what do you think it was?

50:18.000 --> 50:20.999
Oh, you think that he called them.

50:21.000 --> 50:24.559
Yeah, and to me that's
a logical conclusion.

50:24.560 --> 50:26.639
He looks like me. He sounds like me.

50:26.640 --> 50:27.719
He's got a cellphone.

50:27.720 --> 50:30.839
I think he might be
impersonating me or something.

50:30.840 --> 50:33.879
Right. I just don't think
that he would do that.

50:33.880 --> 50:36.462
Do you think you know him that well?

50:37.200 --> 50:40.559
Well, I mean I know him a
little better than you do.

50:40.560 --> 50:42.585
You've never met him.

50:43.200 --> 50:44.319
But I mean it's weird.

50:44.320 --> 50:47.300
I can totally ask him if you want.

50:47.320 --> 50:48.599
No, that's okay.

50:48.600 --> 50:49.919
- It's just...
- Okay.

50:49.920 --> 50:51.279
- It's just a weird thing.
- Okay.

50:51.280 --> 50:53.020
It is weird.

50:56.280 --> 50:58.959
I'm going to go to the store.
Do you want me to get you anything?

50:58.960 --> 51:01.719
Uh, no. I'm good.

51:01.720 --> 51:04.639
- Thanks.
- Well, you can come if you want.

51:04.640 --> 51:07.950
Do you mind if I just hang out here?

51:10.120 --> 51:11.479
- Of course not.
- Okay.

51:11.480 --> 51:13.220
Okay.

51:59.840 --> 52:01.799
Hey, babe.

52:01.800 --> 52:03.519
Uh, sorry.

52:03.520 --> 52:05.226
Great.

52:34.080 --> 52:35.839
Hey.

52:35.840 --> 52:37.799
Is this a bad time?

52:37.800 --> 52:38.879
No, no.

52:38.880 --> 52:42.623
I was, doing some sit-ups.

52:45.440 --> 52:47.271
I need to talk to you.

52:48.000 --> 52:49.239
What do you want to talk about?

52:49.240 --> 52:51.629
What happened the
last time I was here.

52:52.960 --> 52:57.039
Yeah, that was obviously
important. Yeah.

52:57.040 --> 53:00.199
Ethan, you're so good at articulating

53:00.200 --> 53:03.439
exactly what it is that I'm feeling

53:03.440 --> 53:06.399
in a way that I can't even do,

53:06.400 --> 53:08.519
and it's everything that
I've been wanting to hear,

53:08.520 --> 53:11.022
but now I don't know what to do.

53:11.080 --> 53:13.344
I can't get it out of my head.

53:20.120 --> 53:25.427
Well, I'm glad I said what you
wanted to hear, you know.

53:29.880 --> 53:33.190
Is there anything else you
wanted to see me about?

53:36.000 --> 53:38.264
[HEAVY BREATHING]

53:49.200 --> 53:50.940
