53:53.800 --> 53:55.825
Me too.

54:01.880 --> 54:04.189
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

55:03.440 --> 55:05.101
Hi.

55:07.120 --> 55:08.985
Where are the groceries?

55:11.200 --> 55:12.559
What?

55:12.560 --> 55:15.222
What about the store? What happened?

55:16.720 --> 55:19.268
- The store was closed.
- Oh.

55:44.160 --> 55:47.266
Hey, how about I make
us a couple of mimosas?

55:49.800 --> 55:53.304
I'm not really in the mood for
