55:53.440 --> 55:56.079
Aw, come on. It'll be fun.

55:56.080 --> 55:58.279
We'll have a drink. We'll relax.

55:58.280 --> 56:00.599
Start this day off right.

56:00.600 --> 56:03.865
Then we can talk about
whatever is bothering you.

56:05.080 --> 56:07.787
You know, that's really good advice.

56:08.320 --> 56:10.982
And I should probably listen to it...

56:12.680 --> 56:15.103
But you're not a real person.

56:20.920 --> 56:23.104
You know you're not real.

56:25.640 --> 56:27.346
Who the hell are you?

56:28.560 --> 56:30.639
What the hell are you?
Are you a fucking robot?

56:30.640 --> 56:35.543
Are you a... Like a spirit?

56:36.280 --> 56:39.759
