58:29.680 --> 58:31.909
[SPRAYING SOUNDS]

58:32.120 --> 58:34.907
Where did you get this sweater?

58:35.080 --> 58:37.025
What?

58:37.120 --> 58:38.999
Where'd you get this?

58:39.000 --> 58:40.639
I don't know. I've always had it.

58:40.640 --> 58:42.839
- Really?
- Yeah, you just...

58:42.840 --> 58:45.229
