calling to thank you

01:12:52.600 --> 01:12:56.079
for your wonderful
recommendation this weekend.

01:12:56.080 --> 01:12:59.959
Maybe next session you can send
us to a fucking holocaust museum.

01:12:59.960 --> 01:13:01.700
Thank you very much.

01:13:10.800 --> 01:13:12.301
[GROANS]

01:13:28.480 --> 01:13:31.199
<i>MAN: All right, so we have to hit
the keys at the exact same time.</i>

01:13:31.200 --> 01:13:32.479
<i>This is a strange exercise.</i>

01:13:32.480 --> 01:13:33.799
<i>On three, okay?</i>

01:13:33.800 --> 01:13:34.999
<i>One...</i>

01:13:35.000 --> 01:13:36.319
<i>- WOMAN: All right.
- MAN: Two.</i>

01:13:36.320 --> 01:13:37.981
<i>Three.</i>

01:13:45.600 --> 01:13:48.467
<i>THERAPIST:
You met in Scottsdale, Arizona.</i>

01:13:48.520 --> 01:13:51.148
<i>We met in Scottsdale, Arizona.</i>

01:13:51.640 --> 01:13:53.879
<i>Madison, you have two sisters, right?</i>

01:13:53.880 --> 01:13:55.519
<i>MAN: Yes, two sisters.</i>

01:13:55.520 --> 01:13:57.479
<i>I'm the middle child,
and my dad wasn't present.</i>

01:13:57.480 --> 01:13:58.599
Why are you here?

01:13:58.600 --> 01:14:01.119
<i>THERAPIST: You were raised in a
predominantly female household</i>

01:14:01.120 --> 01:14:03.349
<i>and you had serious...</i>

01:14:08.600 --> 01:14:11.228
Ethan and Sophie.

01:14:22.440 --> 01:14:24.146
Holy shit!

